==Schedule==
The schedule of the competition was as follows.<ref name="calendar">{{cite web|url=http://www.cafonline.com/Portals/0/AAG%20MEN/Flash%20CL%20EN%202015-%20Web.pdf|title=Orange CAF CL FINAL 2015: CAF Flash Magazine|publisher=CAF}}</ref> For the first time, some rounds of matches were officially scheduled in midweek (in ''italics'') instead of on weekends.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cafonline.com/en-US/NewsCenter/News/NewsDetails?id=ETXch2u8U02jVFtKs164ng%3d%3d|title=CAF clubs create history with midweek games|publisher=CAF|date=18 April 2016}}</ref>

